1
00:00:06,630 --> 00:00:08,150
[Yizhou]
Yizhou

2
00:00:08,520 --> 00:00:09,920
holds Brocade Weaving Competition,

3
00:00:10,270 --> 00:00:11,190
on the ninth day of the tenth month.

4
00:00:45,560 --> 00:00:47,150
[Young Ji Yingying]
The craft of Shu brocade began in the Spring and Autumn era

5
00:00:47,150 --> 00:00:48,520
and flourished greatly in the Han and Tang dynasties.

6
00:00:49,150 --> 00:00:51,110
It takes its name from its birthplace, the land of Shu.

7
00:00:51,520 --> 00:00:52,240
During the Tang dynasty,

8
00:00:52,590 --> 00:00:55,000
Shu brocade was greatly prized by nobles and prosperous merchants alike.

9
00:00:55,110 --> 00:00:56,040
It was even used as currency

10
00:00:56,040 --> 00:00:57,200
within the military,

11
00:00:58,400 --> 00:01:00,470
and for a time, its value rose to extraordinary heights.

12
00:01:01,000 --> 00:01:02,840
[Deity Tablet of Leizhu]
An inch of Shu brocade holds the worth of pure gold.

13
00:01:04,190 --> 00:01:05,120
My father

14
00:01:05,120 --> 00:01:07,870
[Mixing dyes]
is renowned as the finest brocade artisan in all of Yizhou.

15
00:01:08,140 --> 00:01:09,430
[Grinding and mixing]
It was he who crafted the most exquisite shade of red

16
00:01:09,430 --> 00:01:10,810
[Dyeing process]
ever seen in Shu.

17
00:01:11,720 --> 00:01:13,480
He devoted himself to mastering the art of dyeing,

18
00:01:13,720 --> 00:01:15,040
[Hanging to dry]
experimenting tirelessly to perfect his hues.

19
00:01:15,190 --> 00:01:16,760
Every step of the process, he insisted upon overseeing with his own eyes.

20
00:01:17,270 --> 00:01:18,270
[Ji Guinan, Ji Yingying's father]
He often said that

21
00:01:18,270 --> 00:01:21,000
to attain the richest and most vivid colors,

22
00:01:21,000 --> 00:01:23,190
[Pattern weaving]
the silk must be washed in the pure waters of Huanhua Creek.

23
00:01:25,940 --> 00:01:28,660
[Pattern transfer]

24
00:01:31,740 --> 00:01:34,500
[Drawing motifs]

25
00:01:36,250 --> 00:01:38,040
[Pattern selection and base tying]

26
00:01:38,260 --> 00:01:39,670
[Weft insertion]

27
00:01:40,360 --> 00:01:43,000
It was the most breathtaking red silk I had ever seen.

28
00:01:43,440 --> 00:01:44,950
It was bold, radiant,

29
00:01:45,310 --> 00:01:46,550
and alive with brilliance.

30
00:01:47,400 --> 00:01:48,800
Father named it...

31
00:01:48,800 --> 00:01:49,400
[Ji]

32
00:01:49,400 --> 00:01:51,160
Shu Red Silk.

33
00:01:51,310 --> 00:01:54,430
[Shu Red Silk, Ji Guinan]

34
00:01:54,950 --> 00:01:55,870
But the silk...

35
00:01:56,800 --> 00:01:58,310
it was too beautiful.

36
00:01:58,310 --> 00:01:58,830
That's my father!

37
00:01:58,830 --> 00:02:00,440
My father became the Brocade Master.

38
00:02:01,270 --> 00:02:02,510
My father became the Brocade Master!

39
00:02:02,630 --> 00:02:05,120
[Ji]
And with its beauty came trouble.

40
00:02:06,160 --> 00:02:07,160
Ji Guinan,

41
00:02:07,680 --> 00:02:09,160
how dare you

42
00:02:09,270 --> 00:02:10,670
present such shoddy brocade

43
00:02:11,080 --> 00:02:13,160
as imperial tribute!

44
00:02:14,170 --> 00:02:14,930
Mr. Liu,

45
00:02:15,320 --> 00:02:17,160
we both inspected the boxes together that day.

46
00:02:17,320 --> 00:02:19,080
I personally examined each one,

47
00:02:19,080 --> 00:02:20,270
[Mr. Liu]
and there was no doubt they were genuine.

48
00:02:21,320 --> 00:02:22,080
Yet,

49
00:02:22,270 --> 00:02:23,470
after being entrusted to the logistics officer,

50
00:02:23,630 --> 00:02:25,720
they mysteriously turned into counterfeit goods overnight at the inn.

51
00:02:26,440 --> 00:02:28,270
There is certainly something foul afoot here.

52
00:02:28,600 --> 00:02:29,160
How insolent!

53
00:02:29,550 --> 00:02:31,830
Are you insinuating that the logistics officer stole the brocade?

54
00:02:32,320 --> 00:02:33,080
Guards!

55
00:02:33,360 --> 00:02:33,830
Yes, sir!

56
00:02:33,880 --> 00:02:34,750
Take him away!

57
00:02:34,800 --> 00:02:35,270
Wait!

58
00:02:36,630 --> 00:02:37,470
Your position

59
00:02:38,030 --> 00:02:40,000
grants you no authority to imprison anyone!

60
00:02:42,240 --> 00:02:43,320
I demand to see the governor

61
00:02:43,600 --> 00:02:44,160
and prove my innocence!

62
00:03:19,320 --> 00:03:20,470
Don't be afraid.

63
00:03:21,600 --> 00:03:22,750
Don't...

64
00:03:29,190 --> 00:03:30,360
Father!

65
00:03:37,360 --> 00:03:38,600
Ji Guinan

66
00:03:38,720 --> 00:03:40,110
is hereby sentenced to immediate execution

67
00:03:40,110 --> 00:03:41,320
for presenting inferior goods as tribute,

68
00:03:41,320 --> 00:03:42,440
deceiving the emperor,

69
00:03:42,470 --> 00:03:44,080
and resisting arrest!

70
00:03:44,080 --> 00:03:45,360
[Logistics Officer]

71
00:03:47,440 --> 00:03:48,270
Yes, sir!

72
00:03:52,960 --> 00:03:53,960
Ji Guinan

73
00:03:54,440 --> 00:03:55,830
has been executed

74
00:03:56,160 --> 00:03:57,670
by the logistics officer

75
00:03:58,000 --> 00:03:59,240
for passing off inferior goods as tribute,

76
00:03:59,830 --> 00:04:01,000
deceiving the emperor,

77
00:04:01,320 --> 00:04:02,550
and resisting arrest!

78
00:04:03,960 --> 00:04:05,750
Seize all

79
00:04:06,110 --> 00:04:07,000
of the Ji family's assets.

80
00:04:07,270 --> 00:04:08,110
Search everywhere!

81
00:04:08,750 --> 00:04:09,320
Yes, sir!

82
00:04:18,480 --> 00:04:20,760
A rabbit cannot slay a tiger with a single bite,

83
00:04:21,880 --> 00:04:23,110
but so long as it remains unseen,

84
00:04:24,320 --> 00:04:26,110
[Young Yang Jinglan]
it can keep gnawing.

85
00:04:27,040 --> 00:04:28,040
One day,

86
00:04:28,760 --> 00:04:30,160
it shall bring down the tiger.

87
00:04:51,570 --> 00:04:52,920
[Young Ji Yaoting]

88
00:04:55,350 --> 00:04:57,140
[Ji Gui]

89
00:05:05,480 --> 00:05:06,110
Report!

90
00:05:10,480 --> 00:05:11,760
We have discovered a robe of Shu Red Silk.

91
00:05:11,760 --> 00:05:13,000
It is most likely a gift from the palace.

92
00:05:14,110 --> 00:05:15,040
That's mine!

93
00:05:15,160 --> 00:05:17,040
My father left it to me!

94
00:05:17,110 --> 00:05:17,440
Let go!

95
00:05:17,440 --> 00:05:17,790
Yingying!

96
00:05:18,350 --> 00:05:19,390
Let go, Yingying!

97
00:05:19,390 --> 00:05:19,790
Let go!

98
00:05:20,110 --> 00:05:20,480
Hey!

99
00:05:20,480 --> 00:05:21,110
Let go!

100
00:05:21,440 --> 00:05:22,070
Father said that

101
00:05:22,270 --> 00:05:23,880
- silk could always be rewoven, - Let go!

102
00:05:23,880 --> 00:05:25,920
but if you are gone as well, then all shall truly be lost!

103
00:05:25,920 --> 00:05:27,040
I said, let go!

104
00:05:29,230 --> 00:05:30,200
Yingying!

105
00:06:17,390 --> 00:06:18,600
Yingying, you can't go!

106
00:06:19,440 --> 00:06:20,040
Yingying!

107
00:06:21,350 --> 00:06:21,790
Hey!

108
00:06:21,790 --> 00:06:22,640
[Young Zhao Xiuyuan]
Xiuyuan,

109
00:06:23,200 --> 00:06:23,790
you can't go!

110
00:06:24,200 --> 00:06:24,920
Father,

111
00:06:24,950 --> 00:06:26,110
please save the Ji family.

112
00:06:27,270 --> 00:06:28,880
What do you know, child?

113
00:06:28,880 --> 00:06:29,920
Please!

114
00:06:29,920 --> 00:06:30,760
Let's go home.

115
00:06:30,920 --> 00:06:32,070
Let's go!

116
00:06:57,360 --> 00:07:00,420
[Sandaoyan]

117
00:07:00,970 --> 00:07:03,640
[Five months later]

118
00:07:06,920 --> 00:07:08,950
This place may be a bit run-down,

119
00:07:10,000 --> 00:07:12,350
but it's the best house I could find.

120
00:07:13,480 --> 00:07:15,000
Mr. Zhao, you are most gracious.

121
00:07:15,920 --> 00:07:16,510
The Ji family

122
00:07:17,270 --> 00:07:19,070
[Mrs. Ji, Ji Yingying's mother]
shall repay you the sum at the earliest opportunity.

123
00:07:19,200 --> 00:07:20,550
There is no need for haste

124
00:07:20,550 --> 00:07:21,670
in repaying the sum.

125
00:07:22,110 --> 00:07:23,760
You, Yingying, and Yaoting

126
00:07:23,760 --> 00:07:24,720
have been granted amnesty.

127
00:07:24,950 --> 00:07:26,550
This marks a new beginning.

128
00:07:26,920 --> 00:07:28,920
From here on, all will get better.

129
00:07:30,480 --> 00:07:31,950
Thank you, Mr. Zhao.

130
00:07:32,970 --> 00:07:36,780
[Ji Guinan's Memorial Tablet]

131
00:07:37,320 --> 00:07:38,070
Guinan,

132
00:07:39,920 --> 00:07:41,230
we have returned home.

133
00:07:42,200 --> 00:07:43,790
Do not worry, Father.

134
00:07:44,600 --> 00:07:47,640
From this day forth, Yaoting and I will be good and obedient to Mother.

135
00:07:55,880 --> 00:07:56,790
Mrs. Ji,

136
00:07:56,920 --> 00:07:58,320
now that you have returned,

137
00:07:58,350 --> 00:07:59,880
we kindly ask that you come out to meet us.

138
00:08:01,640 --> 00:08:02,480
[Signed by Ji's Brocade Workshop and Liu's Brocade Store]
Mrs. Ji,

139
00:08:02,550 --> 00:08:03,720
how about

140
00:08:03,920 --> 00:08:05,830
settling the debts?

141
00:08:07,350 --> 00:08:08,160
Everyone,

142
00:08:08,790 --> 00:08:11,390
the Ji family will repay the money.

143
00:08:11,760 --> 00:08:12,640
However,

144
00:08:12,920 --> 00:08:14,110
with our assets having been seized,

145
00:08:14,200 --> 00:08:15,550
we are left with nothing.

146
00:08:16,110 --> 00:08:18,880
Please give us a little more time.

147
00:08:18,880 --> 00:08:21,720
I have thought of a solution for you.

148
00:08:22,510 --> 00:08:25,320
I have already discussed it with the other creditors.

149
00:08:25,640 --> 00:08:26,720
If you give me

150
00:08:27,200 --> 00:08:30,200
the formula for Shu Red Silk,

151
00:08:30,510 --> 00:08:31,390
we will write off

152
00:08:31,830 --> 00:08:33,200
all your debts,

153
00:08:33,400 --> 00:08:34,880
and I will even settle what you owe

154
00:08:34,880 --> 00:08:36,520
to the others.

155
00:08:36,520 --> 00:08:37,710
My father was convicted,

156
00:08:37,790 --> 00:08:39,200
and all that we had was stripped away.

157
00:08:39,520 --> 00:08:41,200
The formula for Shu Red Silk was not there.

158
00:08:41,350 --> 00:08:42,080
Ting!

159
00:08:42,200 --> 00:08:43,790
When my father was alive,

160
00:08:43,790 --> 00:08:45,200
he treated you all with generosity.

161
00:08:45,470 --> 00:08:47,200
Yet now you place such pressure upon us.

162
00:08:47,350 --> 00:08:48,320
If this were to be made known,

163
00:08:48,320 --> 00:08:49,710
do you not fear for your reputation?

164
00:08:50,550 --> 00:08:52,400
Can reputation fill our stomachs?

165
00:08:53,200 --> 00:08:54,350
Either settle the debt,

166
00:08:55,110 --> 00:08:57,110
or surrender the formula.

167
00:08:57,670 --> 00:08:59,280
I, Zhao Xiuyuan, am willing to act as their guarantor.

168
00:08:59,960 --> 00:09:02,030
Might you allow us some more time?

169
00:09:02,640 --> 00:09:05,400
We are here to collect debts owed by the Ji family.

170
00:09:05,400 --> 00:09:07,590
What business is it of yours, an outsider, to interfere?

171
00:09:09,400 --> 00:09:10,320
Mr. Zhao!

172
00:09:11,470 --> 00:09:13,280
If you are unable to repay the debts,

173
00:09:14,440 --> 00:09:15,400
then perhaps you should sell yourselves

174
00:09:16,000 --> 00:09:18,000
to settle the matter.

175
00:09:18,790 --> 00:09:19,400
Take them away!

176
00:09:20,840 --> 00:09:21,840
What are you doing?

177
00:09:21,910 --> 00:09:23,110
Hey, what are you doing?

178
00:09:23,110 --> 00:09:23,640
No!

179
00:09:23,640 --> 00:09:25,520
- What are you doing? Stop! - Let go of me!

180
00:09:25,760 --> 00:09:26,550
Let go of me!

181
00:09:26,550 --> 00:09:27,400
Hey!

182
00:09:27,640 --> 00:09:28,470
Let go!

183
00:09:30,910 --> 00:09:31,760
Stop!

184
00:09:31,840 --> 00:09:32,910
Mother!

185
00:09:33,550 --> 00:09:34,670
Stop!

186
00:09:35,150 --> 00:09:37,080
Since you refused to provide us a way out,

187
00:09:37,470 --> 00:09:38,320
we may as well end our lives

188
00:09:38,590 --> 00:09:39,760
here and now.

189
00:09:39,760 --> 00:09:40,640
Mother.

190
00:09:40,640 --> 00:09:42,110
Let the public witness

191
00:09:42,440 --> 00:09:45,030
your cruelty toward a widow and her children.

192
00:09:45,230 --> 00:09:47,400
We shall see who will be bold enough to do business with you after today.

193
00:09:50,320 --> 00:09:51,150
That's right!

194
00:09:57,080 --> 00:09:57,760
Very well.

195
00:09:58,200 --> 00:09:59,440
I shall desist for now.

196
00:10:00,520 --> 00:10:01,350
The sum shall be treated

197
00:10:02,000 --> 00:10:03,670
as a loan,

198
00:10:04,400 --> 00:10:05,590
with interest set at five percent.

199
00:10:06,550 --> 00:10:07,880
From hereon,

200
00:10:08,200 --> 00:10:09,710
the interest must be paid annually.

201
00:10:10,520 --> 00:10:11,960
Should you miss even one payment,

202
00:10:14,280 --> 00:10:16,400
do not blame us for taking the matter to the authorities

203
00:10:16,670 --> 00:10:17,880
and having you sell yourselves

204
00:10:18,520 --> 00:10:19,910
in repayment.

205
00:10:20,550 --> 00:10:21,150
Let's go!

206
00:10:27,440 --> 00:10:28,280
Mother?

207
00:10:28,440 --> 00:10:29,280
Mother!

208
00:10:29,470 --> 00:10:30,000
Hey,

209
00:10:30,030 --> 00:10:30,640
Mother!

210
00:10:31,000 --> 00:10:32,280
Mother, are you okay?

211
00:10:32,470 --> 00:10:33,110
Mother?

212
00:10:33,110 --> 00:10:34,110
Mother!

213
00:10:34,320 --> 00:10:35,150
I'm fine.

214
00:10:35,280 --> 00:10:36,110
I'm really fine.

215
00:10:36,710 --> 00:10:38,030
Are you hurt?

216
00:10:38,030 --> 00:10:39,200
No.

217
00:10:39,670 --> 00:10:40,520
We're okay, Mother.

218
00:10:40,640 --> 00:10:41,150
No.

219
00:10:41,280 --> 00:10:42,110
That's good.

220
00:10:42,640 --> 00:10:43,670
That's really good.

221
00:10:44,150 --> 00:10:45,200
That's good.

222
00:10:48,200 --> 00:10:48,910
Mother,

223
00:10:49,760 --> 00:10:51,590
let me help you back inside so you may rest.

224
00:10:53,440 --> 00:10:54,000
Okay.

225
00:11:16,710 --> 00:11:18,550
With the departure of the cold winter,

226
00:11:18,760 --> 00:11:20,000
the first yellow buds of spring begin to bloom.

227
00:11:20,840 --> 00:11:21,590
Yingying,

228
00:11:21,760 --> 00:11:23,080
I hope that all misfortune is left behind,

229
00:11:23,400 --> 00:11:24,520
and that you may start anew.

230
00:11:33,150 --> 00:11:38,900
[Brocade Odyssey]

231
00:11:40,220 --> 00:11:42,980
[Eight years later Huanhua Creek]

232
00:11:46,630 --> 00:11:50,020
[At the far west of Huanhua Creek, one finds solitude amidst the lush greenery]

233
00:11:51,140 --> 00:11:52,990
[Episode One]

234
00:12:18,650 --> 00:12:21,820
[Ji Yingying]

235
00:12:37,680 --> 00:12:39,440
[Mr. Chen, Yingxi Dyehouse]

236
00:12:40,280 --> 00:12:43,870
[Mr. Sheng, Cailuan Dyehouse]

237
00:12:47,710 --> 00:12:51,080
Time to wash the silk!

238
00:12:55,600 --> 00:12:56,990
[Ms. Zhu, known as Pin, daughter of Luoxia Dyehouse]

239
00:13:15,320 --> 00:13:17,150
The Hua family is here! Run!

240
00:13:17,150 --> 00:13:18,320
Hurry, pack up!

241
00:13:18,320 --> 00:13:18,590
Quick!

242
00:13:19,080 --> 00:13:19,910
No one else is permitted here

243
00:13:19,910 --> 00:13:21,150
when the Hua family wants to wash their silk.

244
00:13:21,150 --> 00:13:22,350
They are far too overbearing!

245
00:13:22,960 --> 00:13:24,280
They have a large dyehouse. You can't cross them.

246
00:13:24,280 --> 00:13:24,760
Ms. Zhu,

247
00:13:24,760 --> 00:13:26,230
help me gather that. Quick!

248
00:13:26,230 --> 00:13:27,110
I'll distract them.

249
00:13:27,440 --> 00:13:28,320
Help me, Yingying!

250
00:13:28,550 --> 00:13:29,320
Thank you!

251
00:13:30,030 --> 00:13:31,000
Hurry! Let's go!

252
00:13:36,110 --> 00:13:37,150
Mr. Hua,

253
00:13:37,590 --> 00:13:38,790
what brings you here?

254
00:13:38,840 --> 00:13:40,080
Surely, you wouldn't want the sun

255
00:13:40,080 --> 00:13:42,320
to rob you of your charm by tanning you, would you?

256
00:13:42,640 --> 00:13:45,590
[Hua Xiangrong, the Hua family's son-in-law]
I have come to see

257
00:13:45,590 --> 00:13:48,640
if anyone dares to wash silk on my family's land without permission.

258
00:13:49,880 --> 00:13:51,030
Do you feel the heat?

259
00:13:51,230 --> 00:13:53,230
Why exert yourself in this sweltering weather

260
00:13:53,230 --> 00:13:54,200
by coming here?

261
00:13:54,320 --> 00:13:54,760
Move aside!

262
00:14:01,200 --> 00:14:02,400
The Ji family has recently made a delivery.

263
00:14:02,400 --> 00:14:03,760
Mr. Hua, perhaps you should go and inspect that instead?

264
00:14:03,760 --> 00:14:04,880
What is there to inspect?

265
00:14:04,880 --> 00:14:06,080
My remarkable wife

266
00:14:06,080 --> 00:14:08,470
oversees all the business matters

267
00:14:08,470 --> 00:14:09,910
flawlessly.

268
00:14:10,520 --> 00:14:11,110
That is certainly the case.

269
00:14:11,110 --> 00:14:13,080
Your wife is the one who oversees all the decisions in your household.

270
00:14:19,910 --> 00:14:21,670
Ji Yingying, are you deliberately obstructing me?

271
00:14:21,960 --> 00:14:22,710
Why would I?

272
00:14:22,960 --> 00:14:24,880
I'm just holding the umbrella for you,

273
00:14:24,880 --> 00:14:26,880
so naturally, I'll go wherever you go.

274
00:14:26,880 --> 00:14:28,350
Oh? So now you follow me wherever I go,

275
00:14:28,710 --> 00:14:29,840
is that it?

276
00:14:29,840 --> 00:14:30,550
Hand it over!

277
00:14:30,760 --> 00:14:31,280
Move aside!

278
00:14:45,280 --> 00:14:48,110
You brats are fortunate to escape unscathed today!

279
00:14:48,200 --> 00:14:48,910
Should anyone dare to sneak in

280
00:14:48,910 --> 00:14:51,790
to wash silk during the day again,

281
00:14:52,710 --> 00:14:54,280
I will have their legs broken!

282
00:14:56,110 --> 00:14:57,590
That's right...!

283
00:14:59,960 --> 00:15:00,710
Ji Yingying,

284
00:15:01,230 --> 00:15:02,150
what are you doing here?

285
00:15:03,320 --> 00:15:03,960
I'm just passing through.

286
00:15:04,230 --> 00:15:05,110
I'll be on my way.

287
00:15:05,110 --> 00:15:06,110
Excuse me.

288
00:15:27,470 --> 00:15:29,400
It is prohibited to ride horses at Huanhua Creek!

289
00:15:29,470 --> 00:15:30,960
A fine steed and a fair lady.

290
00:15:31,030 --> 00:15:32,280
Such a beautiful day too.

291
00:15:32,640 --> 00:15:35,640
[Sang Shisi, Chief Sang's son]
Would the fair young lady grace me with her company for a ride?

292
00:15:40,640 --> 00:15:41,400
You gave me quite a fright!

293
00:15:41,400 --> 00:15:42,350
Goodness,

294
00:15:42,840 --> 00:15:43,880
I very nearly fell.

295
00:15:46,110 --> 00:15:47,000
You're so

296
00:15:47,150 --> 00:15:48,150
beautiful.

297
00:15:48,440 --> 00:15:49,470
Allow me to take you to the city

298
00:15:49,670 --> 00:15:50,880
for a bit of merriment.

299
00:15:51,320 --> 00:15:52,030
Scoundrel.

300
00:15:52,150 --> 00:15:53,030
Thug. Quick, run!

301
00:15:53,030 --> 00:15:53,880
Yingying!

302
00:15:55,640 --> 00:15:56,200
Hurry...!

303
00:15:56,200 --> 00:15:57,710
They are harassing her.

304
00:15:58,760 --> 00:16:01,400
How dare you come to Sandaoyan to harass the ladies?

305
00:16:02,280 --> 00:16:03,960
It seems to me

306
00:16:03,960 --> 00:16:04,760
you have

307
00:16:04,760 --> 00:16:06,790
no fear of death!

308
00:16:06,960 --> 00:16:08,320
That's right...!

309
00:16:08,640 --> 00:16:10,030
Did you just threaten me?

310
00:16:10,350 --> 00:16:11,590
Do you know who you are speaking to?

311
00:16:11,590 --> 00:16:12,760
How dare you speak to me in this way!

312
00:16:12,760 --> 00:16:13,440
Listen here.

313
00:16:13,440 --> 00:16:14,440
I'll hit whoever I please.

314
00:16:14,440 --> 00:16:16,200
Why should I care who you are?

315
00:16:16,200 --> 00:16:17,150
Hit him!

316
00:16:33,870 --> 00:16:35,530
[Yang Jinglan]

317
00:16:35,550 --> 00:16:36,350
Mr. Yang,

318
00:16:36,400 --> 00:16:38,320
out of kindness, I invited you to join me in seeing such beauties.

319
00:16:38,760 --> 00:16:39,840
Why did you repay me with a kick?

320
00:16:40,350 --> 00:16:41,590
Touch my horse one more time,

321
00:16:42,230 --> 00:16:43,710
and I'll make sure you meet a watery end.

322
00:16:43,710 --> 00:16:45,320
It was merely a ride.

323
00:16:45,320 --> 00:16:46,320
You... Yes.

324
00:16:46,590 --> 00:16:47,840
They hit your horse.

325
00:16:47,840 --> 00:16:48,400
That one...!

326
00:16:48,670 --> 00:16:50,520
The lady in pink. She is their leader.

327
00:16:52,840 --> 00:16:53,550
You missed.

328
00:17:06,230 --> 00:17:07,040
Is this yours?

329
00:17:09,190 --> 00:17:10,710
Thank you for picking up my flower.

330
00:17:11,950 --> 00:17:13,160
Had I not arrived in time,

331
00:17:13,950 --> 00:17:15,070
he would have died here.

332
00:17:15,070 --> 00:17:15,640
That's right!

333
00:17:16,160 --> 00:17:17,950
He was the one who harassed the ladies first.

334
00:17:17,950 --> 00:17:19,310
If I hadn't intervened,

335
00:17:19,880 --> 00:17:21,190
he would have ended up in jail.

336
00:17:22,590 --> 00:17:23,560
If that's the case,

337
00:17:23,880 --> 00:17:24,760
he certainly deserves to get hit.

338
00:17:25,310 --> 00:17:26,000
What, Mr. Yang?

339
00:17:26,000 --> 00:17:27,520
Why are you siding with outsiders?

340
00:17:28,310 --> 00:17:28,950
Yet,

341
00:17:29,520 --> 00:17:31,800
it was you lot who hit my horse.

342
00:17:33,230 --> 00:17:33,710
That's right.

343
00:17:34,350 --> 00:17:35,190
I'm sorry.

344
00:17:35,400 --> 00:17:36,430
It never mentioned that

345
00:17:36,430 --> 00:17:38,160
it was your horse when we hit it.

346
00:17:38,160 --> 00:17:40,310
Horses can't speak, after all.

347
00:17:40,310 --> 00:17:41,760
We wouldn't have done it

348
00:17:41,760 --> 00:17:42,950
if it had told us it belonged to you.

349
00:17:42,950 --> 00:17:44,040
Exactly.

350
00:17:50,590 --> 00:17:51,230
Yingying,

351
00:17:52,160 --> 00:17:53,070
what are you doing?

352
00:17:53,710 --> 00:17:55,070
With your way with words, miss,

353
00:17:55,280 --> 00:17:56,590
I wonder if you could teach

354
00:17:56,800 --> 00:17:57,880
my horse to talk.

355
00:18:02,560 --> 00:18:03,560
Put her down!

356
00:18:04,430 --> 00:18:05,000
Put her down!

357
00:18:05,000 --> 00:18:05,640
Now!

358
00:18:12,640 --> 00:18:14,160
I can't teach horses to speak,

359
00:18:14,280 --> 00:18:15,950
but I certainly can teach humans.

360
00:18:18,230 --> 00:18:19,560
Humans have self-control,

361
00:18:20,430 --> 00:18:21,000
but horses

362
00:18:21,520 --> 00:18:22,760
do not.

363
00:18:23,680 --> 00:18:25,520
If you're going to hit someone, stay away from the horses.

364
00:18:25,830 --> 00:18:28,040
I won't always arrive in time.

365
00:18:35,520 --> 00:18:36,350
Next time?

366
00:18:36,590 --> 00:18:38,680
Well, that will depend on who is the rider.

367
00:18:38,680 --> 00:18:39,470
Exactly!

368
00:18:43,330 --> 00:18:44,010
My silk.

369
00:18:53,810 --> 00:18:57,260
[Huanhua Dyeing Workshop]

370
00:18:58,430 --> 00:19:00,070
Life is what I seek,

371
00:19:00,430 --> 00:19:02,310
and righteousness is also my desire.

372
00:19:02,760 --> 00:19:04,110
Yet, these two cannot coexist.

373
00:19:04,640 --> 00:19:06,760
[Ji Yaoting, Ji Yiying's brother ]
One must forsake life for righteousness.

374
00:19:13,520 --> 00:19:15,470
This is all we have left at home.

375
00:19:16,070 --> 00:19:17,400
Just make do for now.

376
00:19:21,160 --> 00:19:22,680
A true gentleman does not seek indulgence.

377
00:19:23,070 --> 00:19:25,110
Guo Kui, even if you're a dog,

378
00:19:25,280 --> 00:19:27,760
there are rules to follow.

379
00:19:28,040 --> 00:19:29,280
To be a gentleman is to not be

380
00:19:29,520 --> 00:19:31,280
overly driven by desire for indulgence.

381
00:19:33,110 --> 00:19:34,830
I'll beat you up if you're being picky! Eat!

382
00:19:37,760 --> 00:19:40,350
Yingying, why are you in such a bad mood?

383
00:19:40,680 --> 00:19:41,880
Who did you argue with?

384
00:19:42,430 --> 00:19:43,310
No one.

385
00:19:43,680 --> 00:19:44,640
I was just in a fight.

386
00:19:46,350 --> 00:19:47,110
With whom?

387
00:19:47,110 --> 00:19:47,950
I don't know.

388
00:19:48,680 --> 00:19:51,160
They dress in fine clothes,

389
00:19:51,160 --> 00:19:52,760
but they have no idea who I am.

390
00:19:54,040 --> 00:19:56,070
Yaoting, we've talked about it before. Stick to the old rule.

391
00:19:56,070 --> 00:19:57,640
If no one comes looking for us, act like nothing happened.

392
00:19:57,640 --> 00:19:59,470
If someone does, take Mother for a walk.

393
00:20:00,230 --> 00:20:00,830
Mr. Ji,

394
00:20:01,950 --> 00:20:02,590
Ms. Ji,

395
00:20:03,400 --> 00:20:04,680
Mrs. Hua is here.

396
00:20:04,920 --> 00:20:06,190
Yaoting, don't worry. I'll see her.

397
00:20:07,350 --> 00:20:09,000
I'll hold her off.

398
00:20:09,430 --> 00:20:09,950
Give me.

399
00:20:17,470 --> 00:20:18,350
Mrs. Hua,

400
00:20:18,760 --> 00:20:20,920
[Hesheng Rice Store]
the silk you ordered are all here.

401
00:20:21,040 --> 00:20:21,880
Kindly check the numbers.

402
00:20:22,090 --> 00:20:24,110
[Huarong, the owner of Hua's Dyehouse]

403
00:20:24,110 --> 00:20:26,680
The color is dull, lacking vibrancy,

404
00:20:27,280 --> 00:20:28,830
and it doesn't have the luster it should.

405
00:20:29,760 --> 00:20:32,920
It doesn't feel smooth either.

406
00:20:35,470 --> 00:20:37,470
Mrs. Hua, take a closer look.

407
00:20:37,560 --> 00:20:39,560
This is the finest mulberry silk of Jiannandao,

408
00:20:39,880 --> 00:20:40,710
with a consistent texture

409
00:20:40,710 --> 00:20:41,710
and a soft luster.

410
00:20:41,880 --> 00:20:43,880
The color is far more vibrant than anything else on the market.

411
00:20:43,880 --> 00:20:44,880
Mr. Ji,

412
00:20:45,070 --> 00:20:46,880
I'll be honest with you.

413
00:20:47,350 --> 00:20:49,230
Business has been tough lately.

414
00:20:50,430 --> 00:20:51,190
A few of the major brocade merchants in Yizhou

415
00:20:51,190 --> 00:20:53,560
have been undercutting prices.

416
00:20:53,640 --> 00:20:54,880
If this continues,

417
00:20:55,160 --> 00:20:57,760
I won't be able to afford your silk anymore.

418
00:20:58,230 --> 00:20:59,470
Trust is the foundation of everything.

419
00:20:59,640 --> 00:21:00,920
Since we've made an agreement,

420
00:21:00,920 --> 00:21:02,310
we should honor it.

421
00:21:02,310 --> 00:21:04,070
That may be your business practice,

422
00:21:04,710 --> 00:21:05,640
but my practice

423
00:21:05,880 --> 00:21:06,800
is to buy it

424
00:21:07,640 --> 00:21:08,880
at five-tenths.

425
00:21:09,310 --> 00:21:10,680
If you don't want to sell, that's your choice.

426
00:21:11,040 --> 00:21:14,040
I'll pay you at the original price for this order,

427
00:21:15,470 --> 00:21:16,470
but don't expect

428
00:21:16,470 --> 00:21:17,520
any more orders

429
00:21:17,640 --> 00:21:19,680
from me after this.

430
00:21:20,430 --> 00:21:22,880
Mrs. Hua, you're aware of my family's situation.

431
00:21:23,040 --> 00:21:24,430
We have to pay you annual interest,

432
00:21:24,430 --> 00:21:25,640
and on top of that, my mother is ill.

433
00:21:25,680 --> 00:21:27,880
Her medicine requires a lot of money.

434
00:21:28,350 --> 00:21:29,470
What about this?

435
00:21:29,880 --> 00:21:31,470
If you're truly in need of money,

436
00:21:32,280 --> 00:21:33,640
I can lend you 20 guan.

437
00:21:33,640 --> 00:21:35,430
We already owe you money.

438
00:21:35,680 --> 00:21:36,590
If we borrow more...

439
00:21:36,590 --> 00:21:37,230
How...

440
00:21:37,230 --> 00:21:39,430
How could we ever manage to pay off what we owe?

441
00:21:39,470 --> 00:21:40,280
Yaoting,

442
00:21:41,760 --> 00:21:43,430
Mrs. Hua is joking.

443
00:21:43,470 --> 00:21:45,230
She won't lend us money anymore.

444
00:21:48,070 --> 00:21:48,880
Mrs. Hua.

445
00:21:50,830 --> 00:21:51,710
Why wouldn't she?

446
00:21:53,040 --> 00:21:54,110
Yaoting, think about it.

447
00:21:54,280 --> 00:21:56,470
We already owe her 50 guan.

448
00:21:56,470 --> 00:21:57,760
If we borrow another 20 guan,

449
00:21:57,880 --> 00:21:59,160
the three percent interest

450
00:21:59,280 --> 00:22:00,160
alone exceeds

451
00:22:00,160 --> 00:22:02,070
our family's annual profit.

452
00:22:02,280 --> 00:22:03,560
If we can't pay her,

453
00:22:03,680 --> 00:22:04,230
our family

454
00:22:04,230 --> 00:22:05,710
will end up as servants to the Hua family.

455
00:22:06,760 --> 00:22:07,710
But Mrs. Hua

456
00:22:08,800 --> 00:22:10,310
is generous,

457
00:22:10,310 --> 00:22:11,310
beautiful, and kind.

458
00:22:11,470 --> 00:22:13,110
She wouldn't force us to sell ourselves,

459
00:22:13,230 --> 00:22:14,920
so of course she wouldn't lend us money,

460
00:22:15,280 --> 00:22:16,280
right, Mrs. Hua?

461
00:22:17,880 --> 00:22:18,680
Alright then.

462
00:22:19,280 --> 00:22:21,160
Since your family doesn't need the money,

463
00:22:21,920 --> 00:22:22,680
I'll adjust this order

464
00:22:23,040 --> 00:22:24,470
to four-tenths of the price.

465
00:22:24,470 --> 00:22:25,280
Mrs. Hua.

466
00:22:25,470 --> 00:22:26,070
Alright.

467
00:22:26,520 --> 00:22:29,110
We'll adjust the order as requested, Mrs. Hua.

468
00:22:29,880 --> 00:22:30,680
This way, please.

469
00:22:37,520 --> 00:22:39,880
Mrs. Hua, the pen and paper are all set.

470
00:22:39,880 --> 00:22:40,880
You can start.

471
00:22:45,070 --> 00:22:45,830
Ji Yingying,

472
00:22:46,280 --> 00:22:47,880
I knew that you were up to no good!

473
00:22:48,110 --> 00:22:49,230
Come in here! Come!

474
00:22:49,230 --> 00:22:49,880
Shh!

475
00:22:50,560 --> 00:22:51,280
Our dog

476
00:22:51,280 --> 00:22:52,950
can't tolerate shouting.

477
00:22:53,070 --> 00:22:53,880
The louder you get,

478
00:22:53,880 --> 00:22:54,880
the faster it will sink its teeth into you.

479
00:22:55,400 --> 00:22:56,520
I'm warning you.

480
00:22:56,680 --> 00:22:58,430
If you deliberately hurt me,

481
00:22:58,520 --> 00:22:59,560
you'll find yourself behind bars!

482
00:23:00,560 --> 00:23:01,310
I'm warning you.

483
00:23:01,310 --> 00:23:02,520
If you deliberately hurt her,

484
00:23:02,520 --> 00:23:03,310
you'll find yourself behind bars!

485
00:23:05,920 --> 00:23:08,430
It said the food in prison is better than at home.

486
00:23:08,470 --> 00:23:09,520
Oh dear!

487
00:23:10,070 --> 00:23:11,230
It's actually willing to go to jail.

488
00:23:12,880 --> 00:23:13,830
What do you want from me

489
00:23:15,110 --> 00:23:16,230
for you send the dog away?

490
00:23:17,280 --> 00:23:18,230
You know it.

491
00:23:21,190 --> 00:23:21,920
Five-tenths.

492
00:23:22,230 --> 00:23:23,430
Tao Yuanming said

493
00:23:23,430 --> 00:23:24,760
not to yield to a simple five-tenths discount.

494
00:23:24,880 --> 00:23:26,190
That's five packets of rice!

495
00:23:26,190 --> 00:23:27,560
Did you even know that?

496
00:23:31,830 --> 00:23:33,950
Six-tenths. Only six-tenths at most!

497
00:23:35,880 --> 00:23:38,000
It said six-tenths isn't even enough to buy its meat.

498
00:23:38,000 --> 00:23:39,230
It still wants to go to jail.

499
00:23:42,160 --> 00:23:44,590
Seven-tenths! Seven-tenths at most!

500
00:23:52,070 --> 00:23:53,110
You should have said that earlier.

501
00:23:53,470 --> 00:23:54,190
[Contracting parties: Huanhua Dyehouse, Hua's Dyehouse]
Deal!

502
00:23:55,040 --> 00:23:55,950
Kindly sign here.

503
00:24:00,830 --> 00:24:02,000
Thank you for your patronage.

504
00:24:02,280 --> 00:24:03,830
Guo Kui, see our guests off!

505
00:24:11,470 --> 00:24:12,000
Yingying,

506
00:24:12,190 --> 00:24:14,280
I know Mrs. Hua is doing this

507
00:24:14,280 --> 00:24:14,830
to force us

508
00:24:14,830 --> 00:24:16,280
to become her servants forever.

509
00:24:16,280 --> 00:24:17,880
What will we do if she refuses to buy

510
00:24:18,430 --> 00:24:20,400
our family's silk

511
00:24:20,400 --> 00:24:21,430
after how you treated her today?

512
00:24:21,760 --> 00:24:23,230
We dyed our silks well.

513
00:24:23,230 --> 00:24:23,880
A three-tenths discount

514
00:24:23,880 --> 00:24:24,760
won't hurt her.

515
00:24:25,190 --> 00:24:26,560
She can be angry,

516
00:24:26,640 --> 00:24:27,830
but she's a businesswoman.

517
00:24:27,830 --> 00:24:29,160
Profit always comes first.

518
00:24:29,190 --> 00:24:30,430
Father always said,

519
00:24:30,430 --> 00:24:31,590
a lasting business is built

520
00:24:31,590 --> 00:24:32,760
when we win people over with virtue.

521
00:24:32,760 --> 00:24:33,800
Father also always said

522
00:24:33,800 --> 00:24:35,590
to reason with reasonable people.

523
00:24:36,400 --> 00:24:37,760
Yaoting, didn't we discuss this?

524
00:24:37,760 --> 00:24:38,470
You handle what's been done,

525
00:24:38,470 --> 00:24:39,560
and I'll take care of what's to come.

526
00:24:39,830 --> 00:24:41,040
Alright...

527
00:24:41,160 --> 00:24:41,920
Mrs. Ji,

528
00:24:42,230 --> 00:24:44,070
I heard you daughter got into a a fight

529
00:24:44,070 --> 00:24:44,760
at Huanhua Creek.

530
00:24:54,560 --> 00:24:55,280
Ting,

531
00:24:55,640 --> 00:24:57,160
fetch my cane.

532
00:24:57,590 --> 00:24:58,350
Don't go.

533
00:24:58,640 --> 00:24:59,400
Mother.

534
00:24:59,400 --> 00:25:00,040
Go now!

535
00:25:01,280 --> 00:25:02,230
You are on your own.

536
00:25:02,590 --> 00:25:03,640
No way.

537
00:25:04,070 --> 00:25:05,000
Ji Yingying, stand there!

538
00:25:05,000 --> 00:25:06,040
Let's die together.

539
00:25:19,800 --> 00:25:20,590
Mother.

540
00:25:20,800 --> 00:25:22,000
She's not mute.

541
00:25:22,160 --> 00:25:23,590
You don't need to defend her.

542
00:25:31,560 --> 00:25:34,640
Mother, I was wrong.

543
00:25:35,190 --> 00:25:36,590
Why don't you punish me?

544
00:25:36,950 --> 00:25:38,000
The physician has spoken

545
00:25:38,000 --> 00:25:38,680
of your condition.

546
00:25:38,680 --> 00:25:40,280
How many times have I told you?

547
00:25:40,830 --> 00:25:41,830
Acting recklessly

548
00:25:41,830 --> 00:25:43,400
and aggressively

549
00:25:43,400 --> 00:25:44,950
will only ruin your reputation.

550
00:25:48,070 --> 00:25:49,190
Tell me.

551
00:25:49,760 --> 00:25:51,800
Do you have the grace of a noble lady at all?

552
00:25:53,800 --> 00:25:54,590
Ji Yingying.

553
00:25:56,190 --> 00:25:56,830
Mother.

554
00:25:57,560 --> 00:25:58,830
Mother...

555
00:25:58,830 --> 00:26:01,590
I'm hungry. My stomach is growling.

556
00:26:01,590 --> 00:26:02,800
I'm so hungry.

557
00:26:03,000 --> 00:26:04,430
I know I've made a mistake.

558
00:26:04,430 --> 00:26:06,000
Please forgive me.

559
00:26:06,350 --> 00:26:07,230
Alright.

560
00:26:07,230 --> 00:26:08,430
Sit down and eat.

561
00:26:09,760 --> 00:26:11,830
I know that you love me most, Mother.

562
00:26:20,160 --> 00:26:21,190
I've been thinking

563
00:26:21,920 --> 00:26:24,400
about how Mrs. Hua has been collecting

564
00:26:24,470 --> 00:26:26,310
our debts for the past eight years.

565
00:26:27,560 --> 00:26:28,640
She's still our only creditor

566
00:26:28,760 --> 00:26:30,590
to this day.

567
00:26:31,190 --> 00:26:32,040
I think she has

568
00:26:32,710 --> 00:26:34,000
other motives.

569
00:26:34,230 --> 00:26:36,000
Have you had enough yet?

570
00:26:36,680 --> 00:26:39,430
Let your brother worry about this.

571
00:26:40,190 --> 00:26:41,590
You're all grown up.

572
00:26:41,590 --> 00:26:43,160
You can't keep acting like you did before.

573
00:26:43,640 --> 00:26:44,310
You also have

574
00:26:44,310 --> 00:26:46,760
an engagement with Mr. Zhao.

575
00:26:47,230 --> 00:26:50,000
Mr. Zhao has been generous to our family over the years.

576
00:26:50,070 --> 00:26:51,590
Don't put him in a difficult position.

577
00:26:51,830 --> 00:26:53,800
Yaoting isn't married yet. I'm not in a hurry.

578
00:26:57,520 --> 00:26:59,680
You cannot refuse what is offered by elders.

579
00:27:08,880 --> 00:27:09,310
Ting.

580
00:27:09,310 --> 00:27:10,280
I will not marry

581
00:27:10,350 --> 00:27:11,950
until I have cleared our debts

582
00:27:12,040 --> 00:27:13,160
and restored our family's honor.

583
00:27:13,680 --> 00:27:14,680
How resolute!

584
00:27:17,880 --> 00:27:19,680
I'm younger, so don't refuse it.

585
00:27:25,280 --> 00:27:26,830
When Heaven bestows great responsibility upon someone,

586
00:27:26,830 --> 00:27:28,230
it first tempers their mind and body

587
00:27:28,230 --> 00:27:29,190
through hardships

588
00:27:29,190 --> 00:27:30,470
to fortify

589
00:27:30,470 --> 00:27:31,310
their character.

590
00:27:31,310 --> 00:27:32,640
Enough...

591
00:27:33,280 --> 00:27:34,950
Ji Yingying, tell me.

592
00:27:35,280 --> 00:27:36,920
Who did you fight with today?

593
00:27:39,640 --> 00:27:41,880
Mother, I didn't fight with anyone today.

594
00:27:41,920 --> 00:27:44,350
Actually, it's because of Huanhua Dyehouse,

595
00:27:44,520 --> 00:27:46,040
Yingxia Dyehouse

596
00:27:46,110 --> 00:27:48,280
and several other dyehouses.

597
00:27:49,160 --> 00:27:50,160
There are just

598
00:27:51,310 --> 00:27:51,920
some...

599
00:27:52,640 --> 00:27:53,950
I'm not entirely sure either.

600
00:27:54,520 --> 00:27:55,680
Guo Kui hasn't eaten yet.

601
00:27:55,680 --> 00:27:57,350
I have to make its dinner.

602
00:27:57,470 --> 00:27:57,950
Ji Yingying!

603
00:27:57,950 --> 00:27:58,560
Guo Kui!

604
00:27:58,710 --> 00:27:59,110
You...!

605
00:27:59,950 --> 00:28:00,760
Time to eat, Guo Kui!

606
00:28:00,760 --> 00:28:01,680
This child.

607
00:28:02,710 --> 00:28:03,230
Ting,

608
00:28:03,710 --> 00:28:05,310
do you know who she fought with today?

609
00:28:05,830 --> 00:28:06,880
I do not.

610
00:28:07,070 --> 00:28:08,920
Find out about it tomorrow,

611
00:28:09,350 --> 00:28:11,640
and make sure to apologize to them properly.

612
00:28:13,110 --> 00:28:13,880
Mother,

613
00:28:14,400 --> 00:28:15,680
Yingying isn't the quiet or gentle type,

614
00:28:15,760 --> 00:28:17,350
but she wouldn't cause trouble without reason.

615
00:28:17,880 --> 00:28:18,950
This matter feels...

616
00:28:20,040 --> 00:28:21,400
Does it even matter who's right or wrong?

617
00:28:21,640 --> 00:28:23,760
Do you not understand too?

618
00:28:23,800 --> 00:28:24,830
I do...

619
00:28:25,800 --> 00:28:26,560
I no longer desire

620
00:28:26,560 --> 00:28:27,680
luxurious things.

621
00:28:28,400 --> 00:28:30,000
All I wish for is for both of you

622
00:28:30,000 --> 00:28:31,520
to live in peace.

623
00:28:34,230 --> 00:28:35,280
Yes, Mother.

624
00:28:36,830 --> 00:28:37,680
Please don't be upset.

625
00:28:39,710 --> 00:28:40,520
Eat your food.

626
00:28:40,950 --> 00:28:42,000
I'll go tomorrow.

627
00:28:55,400 --> 00:28:56,640
Mr. Yang,

628
00:28:57,190 --> 00:28:58,680
I know

629
00:28:59,310 --> 00:29:00,640
I've failed you.

630
00:29:00,800 --> 00:29:03,280
You trusted me

631
00:29:03,400 --> 00:29:05,310
with looking after your mentor,

632
00:29:05,920 --> 00:29:07,430
but he's gone now.

633
00:29:09,000 --> 00:29:10,000
Three brocade officers

634
00:29:10,000 --> 00:29:11,350
have died

635
00:29:12,310 --> 00:29:14,040
in Yizhou alone.

636
00:29:15,310 --> 00:29:16,800
He could have chosen any path.

637
00:29:16,800 --> 00:29:18,040
Why choose to be a brocade officer?

638
00:29:18,040 --> 00:29:19,000
I don't...

639
00:29:19,000 --> 00:29:21,040
What was it that he wanted you to pass on to me?

640
00:29:25,000 --> 00:29:25,920
He told me

641
00:29:26,640 --> 00:29:29,000
to pass this on to you

642
00:29:29,000 --> 00:29:30,560
when I saw you again.

643
00:29:34,310 --> 00:29:36,310
This is your best friend in Yizhou.

644
00:29:36,590 --> 00:29:37,590
What is so good about him?

645
00:29:37,920 --> 00:29:39,110
He trusts me.

646
00:29:39,940 --> 00:29:40,590
[Zhu Gehong]

647
00:29:40,590 --> 00:29:41,430
What message did Mr. Shen

648
00:29:41,760 --> 00:29:43,350
leave for you then?

649
00:29:43,430 --> 00:29:44,920
Do I have to report to you?

650
00:29:46,350 --> 00:29:47,560
I forgot my place.

651
00:29:48,950 --> 00:29:50,560
What are your plans for tomorrow?

652
00:29:50,760 --> 00:29:52,040
Are you going home or...?

653
00:29:53,190 --> 00:29:54,590
I am meeting a friend.

654
00:29:55,040 --> 00:29:56,760
You have friends in Yizhou?

655
00:30:07,920 --> 00:30:09,110
The messenger only mentioned that

656
00:30:09,310 --> 00:30:10,470
soldiers surrounded your house.

657
00:30:10,760 --> 00:30:12,070
Perhaps there is a misunderstanding.

658
00:30:18,190 --> 00:30:19,160
You again?

659
00:30:19,280 --> 00:30:20,040
It's you!

660
00:30:20,470 --> 00:30:22,000
Something urgent came up at home!

661
00:30:22,520 --> 00:30:23,950
Please give me a lift.

662
00:30:35,280 --> 00:30:36,950
If my family makes it through this crisis,

663
00:30:37,880 --> 00:30:39,680
I'll be your friend.

664
00:30:50,310 --> 00:30:51,520
A future friend!

665
00:31:03,560 --> 00:31:04,520
[Huanhua Dyehouse]
Tell Ji Yingying to come out!

666
00:31:07,160 --> 00:31:08,070
Ji Yingying, show yourself!

667
00:31:08,280 --> 00:31:08,560
Ms. Ji!

668
00:31:08,560 --> 00:31:09,430
Ji Yingying, I know you're in there!

669
00:31:09,430 --> 00:31:09,880
Ms. Ji,

670
00:31:10,070 --> 00:31:11,040
what should we do now?

671
00:31:11,040 --> 00:31:11,470
Open up!

672
00:31:11,470 --> 00:31:12,350
Now I see why

673
00:31:12,350 --> 00:31:14,160
Mrs. Ji asked me who you were fighting with.

674
00:31:14,280 --> 00:31:15,430
No one knows.

675
00:31:15,560 --> 00:31:17,040
It turns out he wasn't from Sandaoyan.

676
00:31:17,110 --> 00:31:18,400
He's Mr. Sang from Yizhou!

677
00:31:19,560 --> 00:31:20,760
What should we do?

678
00:31:20,760 --> 00:31:22,830
Mrs. Ji and Mr. Ji aren't home right now!

679
00:31:22,830 --> 00:31:23,950
They are out restocking!

680
00:31:24,280 --> 00:31:24,920
Don't worry, Gui.

681
00:31:24,920 --> 00:31:25,920
I'm here!

682
00:31:27,710 --> 00:31:30,040
Wait... Ms. Ji, what are you looking for?

683
00:31:30,680 --> 00:31:31,950
I'm looking for a useful tool.

684
00:31:32,160 --> 00:31:32,950
Open up!

685
00:31:34,160 --> 00:31:36,350
I'm dying!

686
00:31:38,880 --> 00:31:40,950
What's with all the commotion early in the morning?

687
00:31:44,470 --> 00:31:47,070
So it turns out Mr. Sang has honored us with a visit!

688
00:31:48,110 --> 00:31:49,430
Are you scared now?

689
00:31:49,680 --> 00:31:50,520
Listen here!

690
00:31:50,520 --> 00:31:52,560
Get on your knees and apologize to me!

691
00:31:52,830 --> 00:31:54,280
I'll spare you this once,

692
00:31:54,280 --> 00:31:55,040
out of generosity.

693
00:31:55,040 --> 00:31:57,430
Thank you for your generosity.

694
00:31:57,430 --> 00:31:58,470
You're truly kind.

695
00:31:58,950 --> 00:31:59,830
But...

696
00:31:59,830 --> 00:32:02,560
From head to toe, or left to right,

697
00:32:02,560 --> 00:32:04,640
I don't see any wounds on you?

698
00:32:04,640 --> 00:32:06,280
Look at my leg! My head!

699
00:32:06,310 --> 00:32:07,040
Here!

700
00:32:07,040 --> 00:32:08,880
This arm! Here! They're all broken!

701
00:32:09,160 --> 00:32:09,640
Does it hurt?

702
00:32:12,800 --> 00:32:13,470
Ms. Ji!

703
00:32:14,310 --> 00:32:15,470
Did I use too much force?

704
00:32:15,640 --> 00:32:16,430
I don't know.

705
00:32:18,040 --> 00:32:18,680
Gui,

706
00:32:19,640 --> 00:32:20,680
I'm bleeding...

707
00:32:20,880 --> 00:32:21,640
You're bleeding!

708
00:32:21,760 --> 00:32:22,680
Bleeding?

709
00:32:22,800 --> 00:32:23,760
I'm bleeding!

710
00:32:24,350 --> 00:32:25,040
Mr. Sang,

711
00:32:25,280 --> 00:32:27,070
Ms. Ji was apologizing earnestly to you!

712
00:32:27,070 --> 00:32:29,070
Aren't you going too far?

713
00:32:29,640 --> 00:32:30,680
Don't blame me!

714
00:32:30,680 --> 00:32:31,710
She hit her head on her own!

715
00:32:33,830 --> 00:32:36,280
I'm an unmarried young woman.

716
00:32:36,280 --> 00:32:38,560
I value my appearance too much to harm myself.

717
00:32:38,560 --> 00:32:40,680
Why would I ruin myself?

718
00:32:40,880 --> 00:32:42,070
Enough with the accusations!

719
00:32:42,070 --> 00:32:43,760
Listen! Y-You...

720
00:32:45,040 --> 00:32:46,520
Mr. Sang is fine?

721
00:32:47,070 --> 00:32:48,400
How can you be even more shameless than me?

722
00:32:48,950 --> 00:32:49,640
Do you want me

723
00:32:49,640 --> 00:32:50,800
to lock you up?

724
00:32:51,070 --> 00:32:51,640
You...

725
00:32:51,640 --> 00:32:53,680
I have a very obvious wound on my head.

726
00:32:53,680 --> 00:32:55,880
Everyone saw it, right?

727
00:32:55,880 --> 00:32:57,310
Yes! We all saw it!

728
00:32:57,310 --> 00:32:58,400
Can you let the officials

729
00:32:58,400 --> 00:32:59,950
check your wounds, then?

730
00:32:59,950 --> 00:33:00,350
I...

731
00:33:00,350 --> 00:33:02,070
We can go to the state magistrate

732
00:33:02,070 --> 00:33:03,710
if you want!

733
00:33:03,950 --> 00:33:06,590
I've heard that Chief Sang is a man of fairness.

734
00:33:06,830 --> 00:33:07,880
I'm sure he'll deliver justice

735
00:33:07,880 --> 00:33:09,310
when he gets back!

736
00:33:09,460 --> 00:33:13,690
[Glutinous rice cake]

737
00:33:14,350 --> 00:33:15,560
It's okay. Let me see.

738
00:33:18,560 --> 00:33:19,350
It's really her.

739
00:33:22,560 --> 00:33:24,040
That's the friend you mentioned?

740
00:33:24,590 --> 00:33:26,400
Ji Yingying, the daughter of the Red Silk Brocade Master.

741
00:33:27,160 --> 00:33:28,350
Do you really know her?

742
00:33:28,710 --> 00:33:29,760
Or is this for a case?

743
00:33:31,760 --> 00:33:32,830
No matter the reason,

744
00:33:33,560 --> 00:33:36,350
aren't you going to help her out of this predicament?

745
00:33:37,400 --> 00:33:38,350
No need.

746
00:33:39,110 --> 00:33:39,680
Look.

747
00:33:40,350 --> 00:33:41,430
Her wound is fake,

748
00:33:41,760 --> 00:33:43,520
but her reaction is certainly convincing.

749
00:33:46,350 --> 00:33:47,230
Don't forget,

750
00:33:47,760 --> 00:33:50,190
you've been instructed to find the Shu Red Silk.

751
00:33:51,830 --> 00:33:52,830
This is the taste I've been after!

752
00:33:53,560 --> 00:33:54,520
I tried making it myself,

753
00:33:54,560 --> 00:33:56,350
but I couldn't get it right. Have a try.

754
00:34:16,150 --> 00:34:18,360
I have made a chance for you.

755
00:34:20,870 --> 00:34:21,710
Mr. Yang?

756
00:34:22,040 --> 00:34:23,560
You've arrived at the perfect moment! Please come.

757
00:34:25,630 --> 00:34:27,120
Be our judge!

758
00:34:27,150 --> 00:34:29,430
Wasn't it her who purposely hit her head just now?

759
00:34:31,190 --> 00:34:32,760
I witnessed everything

760
00:34:32,840 --> 00:34:35,360
that happened just now.

761
00:34:37,520 --> 00:34:38,600
I think...

762
00:34:39,950 --> 00:34:42,000
Chief Sang will be back in two days.

763
00:34:42,000 --> 00:34:42,800
I wouldn't cause a scene

764
00:34:42,800 --> 00:34:44,040
if I were you.

765
00:34:44,040 --> 00:34:44,840
You'd get a beating.

766
00:34:45,230 --> 00:34:46,360
Why would I get a beating?

767
00:34:47,760 --> 00:34:49,520
Look here. Between you two,

768
00:34:49,800 --> 00:34:51,360
who would your father believe?

769
00:34:51,760 --> 00:34:52,950
But I'm wrapped up like this...

770
00:34:53,000 --> 00:34:54,560
You can trick everyone else,

771
00:34:54,630 --> 00:34:56,430
but you can't fool your father or me.

772
00:34:59,000 --> 00:35:00,840
Fine! Just you wait!

773
00:35:01,320 --> 00:35:02,190
This is not over!

774
00:35:03,710 --> 00:35:04,120
Let's go!

775
00:35:04,560 --> 00:35:05,560
Take care, Mr. Sang!

776
00:35:16,040 --> 00:35:16,630
Everyone...

777
00:35:17,230 --> 00:35:18,560
They have already left.

778
00:35:19,320 --> 00:35:20,800
Haven't you seen enough?

779
00:35:20,950 --> 00:35:22,280
Should I have Mr. Sang

780
00:35:22,280 --> 00:35:24,080
go to your home and create trouble?

781
00:35:24,910 --> 00:35:25,560
Come on. Let's go home,

782
00:35:25,560 --> 00:35:26,150
Gui!

783
00:35:28,080 --> 00:35:28,600
Sir!

784
00:35:28,910 --> 00:35:29,430
Sir,

785
00:35:30,520 --> 00:35:32,630
I accidentally broke a bowl earlier

786
00:35:32,800 --> 00:35:34,040
and don't have enough money with me.

787
00:35:34,190 --> 00:35:36,230
Could I trouble you to pay for it on my behalf?

788
00:35:37,800 --> 00:35:38,950
If it's inconvenient for you,

789
00:35:39,520 --> 00:35:41,430
I'll have to ask Mr. Sang

790
00:35:41,430 --> 00:35:43,190
to come back and pay it for me.

791
00:35:52,150 --> 00:35:53,670
Thank you.

792
00:35:59,040 --> 00:35:59,840
Ms. Ji,

793
00:36:00,390 --> 00:36:01,430
every action has its cause.

794
00:36:01,950 --> 00:36:04,000
If Mr. Hua hadn't mentioned the beauty of the view

795
00:36:04,150 --> 00:36:05,560
at Huanhua Creek,

796
00:36:05,600 --> 00:36:07,910
Shisi wouldn't have insisted to welcome me there,

797
00:36:08,360 --> 00:36:09,630
and none of this misunderstanding would have occurred.

798
00:36:10,040 --> 00:36:10,760
The Hua family?

799
00:36:12,910 --> 00:36:14,190
No surprise there.

800
00:36:14,950 --> 00:36:16,120
In that case,

801
00:36:16,190 --> 00:36:17,280
I'll have to trouble you

802
00:36:17,280 --> 00:36:18,710
to speak with Mr. Sang

803
00:36:18,710 --> 00:36:20,760
so he doesn't hold anything against us folks from Sandaoyan.

804
00:36:21,950 --> 00:36:22,910
What do I get out of it?

805
00:36:26,800 --> 00:36:27,710
Good things

806
00:36:27,710 --> 00:36:28,760
come to those who do good!

807
00:36:29,950 --> 00:36:31,190
The speed that it dries...

808
00:36:31,430 --> 00:36:32,230
This color...

809
00:36:32,670 --> 00:36:33,670
Is that dye

810
00:36:33,670 --> 00:36:35,230
on your forehead?

811
00:36:36,000 --> 00:36:36,950
You've got guts

812
00:36:37,280 --> 00:36:38,630
tricking Mr. Sang like that.

813
00:36:39,600 --> 00:36:41,360
What do you want?

814
00:36:42,710 --> 00:36:43,760
I lent you a hand.

815
00:36:44,120 --> 00:36:46,360
The least you can do is invite me for a drink.

816
00:36:47,390 --> 00:36:48,630
Deal. Please, step inside.

817
00:36:50,280 --> 00:36:51,040
Hold on!

818
00:37:01,360 --> 00:37:02,840
Sir, here's your water.

819
00:37:05,560 --> 00:37:06,560
You want me to drink here?

820
00:37:07,520 --> 00:37:08,520
It's my family's rules.

821
00:37:08,560 --> 00:37:09,950
It's custom to have a drink once you're inside.

822
00:37:11,630 --> 00:37:12,190
Okay.

823
00:37:21,150 --> 00:37:21,950
Alright.

824
00:37:22,840 --> 00:37:24,520
We're square. Please leave.

825
00:37:25,560 --> 00:37:26,760
I haven't got in.

826
00:37:27,430 --> 00:37:28,520
You wanted to come in.

827
00:37:28,520 --> 00:37:29,560
I let you.

828
00:37:29,560 --> 00:37:30,390
You wanted a drink.

829
00:37:30,390 --> 00:37:31,600
I poured you one.

830
00:37:32,000 --> 00:37:33,150
Thanks for your assistance.

831
00:37:33,150 --> 00:37:34,000
Pardon me for not seeing you out.

832
00:37:34,390 --> 00:37:36,120
Wait! I helped you!

833
00:37:36,120 --> 00:37:36,950
Thank you.

834
00:37:39,560 --> 00:37:40,360
Thank you for your help.

835
00:37:42,360 --> 00:37:42,950
Ms. Ji?

836
00:37:43,710 --> 00:37:44,320
Ms. Ji!

837
00:37:44,870 --> 00:37:45,670
Hey!

838
00:37:46,150 --> 00:37:47,670
You left me outside!

839
00:37:48,760 --> 00:37:49,560
Ms. Ji!

840
00:38:00,190 --> 00:38:01,190
Slow down, Mother.

841
00:38:03,800 --> 00:38:04,320
Stand right there!

842
00:38:07,280 --> 00:38:07,910
Mother!

843
00:38:08,190 --> 00:38:10,320
I didn't get into a fight. I really didn't!

844
00:38:12,040 --> 00:38:12,670
- You... - Yingying,

845
00:38:13,230 --> 00:38:14,120
you're injured!

846
00:38:15,520 --> 00:38:16,280
Oh, no. No!

847
00:38:16,430 --> 00:38:17,470
It's fake!

848
00:38:17,950 --> 00:38:19,120
I'm not hurt at all.

849
00:38:21,120 --> 00:38:21,840
It's fake?

850
