855
00:38:40,190 --> 00:38:40,910
Mother,

856
00:38:40,910 --> 00:38:42,190
Sang Shisi came here

857
00:38:42,230 --> 00:38:43,560
because Mrs. Hua provoked him.

858
00:38:43,630 --> 00:38:44,950
Even if Sang Shisi is willing to let it go,

859
00:38:44,950 --> 00:38:46,320
Mrs. Hua won't let this slide.

860
00:38:46,630 --> 00:38:47,120
Yaoting,

861
00:38:47,150 --> 00:38:48,520
we must come up with a plan to deal with her.

862
00:38:49,470 --> 00:38:50,190
Ji Yingying!

863
00:38:50,950 --> 00:38:52,280
Can't you just let this be?

864
00:38:52,840 --> 00:38:54,120
Must you always fight everything

865
00:38:54,120 --> 00:38:55,280
because of your nature?

866
00:38:55,910 --> 00:38:56,670
Mrs. Hua

867
00:38:56,670 --> 00:38:58,600
dominates the market with no shame,

868
00:38:58,800 --> 00:38:59,360
yet she targets us specifically.

869
00:38:59,360 --> 00:39:01,230
Why?

870
00:39:01,630 --> 00:39:03,470
You think I'm the cause of all this?

871
00:39:04,000 --> 00:39:05,430
Because I wouldn't submit,

872
00:39:05,470 --> 00:39:07,120
